OL,3,CBlue badge holder 'furious' she was
OL,4,Casked to 'prove disability'
OL,6,FA blue badge holder says she is
OL,7,F"furious" after being asked to "prove
OL,8,Fshe was disabled" while trying to
OL,9,Fappeal a parking fine.
OL,11,FNicola Burnett, from Burpham, Surrey
OL,12,Fhad parked on a double yellow line at
OL,13,FThe Royal Surrey Hospital after being
OL,14,Funable to find a free disabled space.
OL,16,FThe 53-year-old was there for an
OL,17,Finterview and when she returned half
OL,18,Fan hour later, she found that she, and
OL,19,Fsix other cars, had been given a
OL,20,Fticket.
