OL,3,CBlue badge holder 'furious' she was
OL,4,Casked to 'prove disability'
OL,6,FBlue badge holders are allowed to park
OL,7,Fon double yellow lines but not in
OL,8,Fprivate car parks, including the one
OL,9,Foutside Nuffield Health operated by
OL,10,FHorizon.
OL,12,FThe fine is for #80, or #48 if paid
OL,13,Fwithin 14 days, which she described as
OL,14,Funaffordable.
OL,16,FMs Burnett said: "I saw I had a
OL,17,Fparking ticket. I was furious. I was
OL,18,Fso angry and so upset, I was crying.
OL,19,FIt felt so wrong.
