OL,3,CBlue badge holder 'furious' she was
OL,4,Casked to 'prove disability'
OL,6,F"I got home and immediately went
OL,7,Fonline to appeal it. I sent the appeal
OL,8,Foff and then, I had an email from
OL,9,F(Horizon) two days later asking me to
OL,10,Fsend medical proof of my disability.
OL,12,F"The very fact that I have a blue
OL,13,Fbadge, and drive a car that I lease
OL,14,Fthrough Motability should be enough
OL,15,Fproof.
OL,17,F"It's very hard to get a blue badge. I
OL,18,Fsent them photographs of my injuries.
OL,19,FI kicked up a storm. I emailed them
OL,20,Fback and said I'm not doing that. I
OL,21,Frefuse to pay the fine.
