OL,3,CBlue badge holder 'furious' she was
OL,4,Casked to 'prove disability'
OL,6,F"I refuse to pay the fine. I'm putting
OL,7,Fmy foot down. I'm fighting this tooth
OL,8,Fand nail now. I suppose it's just the
OL,9,Fprinciple of it."
OL,11,FMs Burnett, who has had a blue badge
OL,12,Ffor about seven years as she has
OL,13,Fmobility issues, does not believe she
OL,14,Fshould have to hand over sensitive
OL,15,Fpersonal data to appeal the fine.
OL,17,FShe added: "I can't walk any distance,
OL,18,FI have to use sticks. Usually, I have
OL,19,Fto have two sticks to walk with but I
OL,20,Fonly had one thinking I wouldn't have
OL,21,Fto walk very far, but I did."
