OL,6,FShe also says she had gone around the
OL,7,Fcar park three times and was unable to
OL,8,Ffind a free disabled space, before
OL,9,Fdeciding to join other disabled car
OL,10,Fusers who had parked on the double
OL,11,Fyellow lines.
OL,13,FA Royal Surrey NHS Foundation Trust
OL,14,Fspokesperson said: "Royal Surrey
OL,15,Fprovides 73 disabled spaces and we
OL,16,Fhave made all the disabled bays as
OL,17,Fclose to the hospital as possible.
