OL,3,CBlue badge holder 'furious' she was
OL,4,Casked to 'prove disability'
OL,6,F"We will also be reinstating nine
OL,7,Fdisabled spaces next to Royal Surrey
OL,8,FCancer Centre in the coming weeks,
OL,9,Fwhich were moved further from the
OL,10,Fhospital building due to essential
OL,11,Fbuilding works. We apologise for any
OL,12,Finconvenience this may have caused.
OL,14,F"We regularly review our car parking
OL,15,Farrangements, and will continue to do
OL,16,Fso to ensure that our services are
OL,17,Feasily accessed by patients and
OL,18,Fvisitors."
