OL,6,FThe Royal Surrey does not manage
OL,7,FHorizon, who issued the ticket. As
OL,8,Fwith other NHS car parks, disabled
OL,9,Fpatients and visitors can receive free
OL,10,Fparking for the duration of their
OL,11,Fattendance at, or visit to, the
OL,12,Fhospital.
OL,14,FHorizon has been approached for
OL,15,Fcomment but did not supply a response
OL,16,Fby the time of publication.
